**Objectives:** [What this phase accomplishes]

**Features Included:**
- [Feature 4] - [Brief description]
- [Feature 5] - [Brief description]

**Success Criteria:**
- [ ] [Measurable completion criterion 1]
- [ ] [Measurable completion criterion 2]

**Deliverables:** [Specific outputs]

